# #Entropy

**#Entropy** → Uncertainty in what a receiver will say. Vocabulary drift over time. Information at namespace boundaries.

When vocabularies collide, entropy measures how much new meaning emerges. Low entropy = predictable blending. High entropy = novel language neither receiver could generate alone.

